<!------------------------------------------------------------------------ingredients----------->

<ul1><font size="4">
<li>0.25 oz active dry yeast</li>
<li>1 tsp white sugar</li>
<li>2.5 cups bread flour</li>
<li>2 tbsp olive oil</li>
<li>1 tsp salt</li>
<li>toppings (you choose)</li>
</ul1></font>
<!-----------------------------------------------------------------instructions--------------------------------->
<ol>
<font size="4">
<li>preheat oven to 450 degrees, dissolve yeast and sugar in warm water. let it sit until creamy.</li>
<li>stir in flour, salt, and oil. Let it rest for 5 minutes.</li>
<li>Place dough onto a floured surface and pat into a round shape</li>
<li>Place dough onto a lightly greased pizza pan and apply toppings. Bake in oven until golden brown.</li>








</ol>
</font>

